CREATE TABLE "ADMISSIONS" (
	row_id INTEGER, 
	subject_id INTEGER, 
	hadm_id INTEGER, 
	admittime TEXT, 
	dischtime TEXT, 
	admission_type TEXT, 
	admission_location TEXT, 
	discharge_location TEXT, 
	insurance TEXT, 
	language TEXT, 
	marital_status TEXT, 
	age INTEGER
)


CREATE TABLE "CHARTEVENTS" (
	row_id INTEGER, 
	subject_id INTEGER, 
	hadm_id INTEGER, 
	stay_id INTEGER, 
	charttime TEXT, 
	itemid INTEGER, 
	valuenum REAL, 
	valueuom TEXT
)


CREATE TABLE "COST" (
	row_id INTEGER, 
	subject_id INTEGER, 
	hadm_id REAL, 
	event_type TEXT, 
	event_id INTEGER, 
	chargetime TEXT, 
	cost REAL
)


CREATE TABLE "DIAGNOSES_ICD" (
	row_id INTEGER, 
	subject_id INTEGER, 
	hadm_id INTEGER, 
	icd_code TEXT, 
	charttime TEXT, 
	FOREIGN KEY(icd_code) REFERENCES "D_ICD_DIAGNOSES" (icd_code), 
	FOREIGN KEY(subject_id) REFERENCES "ADMISSIONS" (subject_id)
)


CREATE TABLE "D_ICD_DIAGNOSES" (
	row_id INTEGER, 
	icd_code TEXT, 
	long_title TEXT
)


CREATE TABLE "D_ICD_PROCEDURES" (
	row_id INTEGER, 
	icd_code TEXT, 
	long_title TEXT
)


CREATE TABLE "D_ITEMS" (
	row_id INTEGER, 
	itemid INTEGER, 
	label TEXT, 
	abbreviation TEXT, 
	linksto TEXT
)


CREATE TABLE "D_LABITEMS" (
	row_id INTEGER, 
	itemid INTEGER, 
	label TEXT
)


CREATE TABLE "ICUSTAYS" (
	row_id INTEGER, 
	subject_id INTEGER, 
	hadm_id INTEGER, 
	stay_id INTEGER, 
	first_careunit TEXT, 
	last_careunit TEXT, 
	intime TEXT, 
	outtime TEXT
)


CREATE TABLE "INPUTEVENTS" (
	row_id INTEGER, 
	subject_id INTEGER, 
	hadm_id INTEGER, 
	stay_id INTEGER, 
	starttime TEXT, 
	itemid REAL, 
	amount REAL
)


CREATE TABLE "LABEVENTS" (
	row_id INTEGER, 
	subject_id INTEGER, 
	hadm_id REAL, 
	itemid INTEGER, 
	charttime TEXT, 
	valuenum REAL, 
	valueuom TEXT
)


CREATE TABLE "MICROBIOLOGYEVENTS" (
	row_id INTEGER, 
	subject_id INTEGER, 
	hadm_id REAL, 
	charttime TEXT, 
	spec_type_desc TEXT, 
	test_name TEXT, 
	org_name TEXT
)


CREATE TABLE "OUTPUTEVENTS" (
	row_id INTEGER, 
	subject_id INTEGER, 
	hadm_id INTEGER, 
	stay_id INTEGER, 
	charttime TEXT, 
	itemid REAL, 
	value REAL
)


CREATE TABLE "PATIENTS" (
	row_id INTEGER, 
	subject_id INTEGER, 
	gender TEXT, 
	dob TEXT, 
	dod TEXT,
